caption: The image features a mosque with a crescent moon and star on top, symbolizing the Islamic faith. The text "Ramadan Kareem" is displayed in front of the mosque, which is a greeting for the Islamic holy month of Ramadan. The text "Hopefully we can meet Ramadan this year" is also present in the image, suggesting a desire to celebrate the holiday with others. The image is associated with the Twitter account "@reallygreatsite".

texts: "Hopefully we can meet ramadan this year"
